=== QUANTUM_GARDEN ===
# id: 6
# title: The Quantum Garden
# chinese_title: 量子花
# category: Discovery
# mode: dungeon

Flowers bloom and wilt in rapid succession inside a containment field, their life cycles compressed into seconds by a localized time distortion. Each blossom is unique, shifting colors in impossible spectrums. A single preserved seed pod sits outside the field, intact and stable.

* [Take the preserved seed pod]
  ~ gain_radical("田")
  "田" (tián) — field, farmland
* [Study the time distortion effect]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "时" (shí) — time
* [Attempt to stabilize the field] {requires: class == 6}
  ~ gain_item("focus_stim")
  "定" (dìng) — to stabilize, fixed
